  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.eclipse.incquery.runtime.rete.eval.AbstractEvaluator
    Use IExpressionEvaluator with an IValueProvider instead.
    org.eclipse.incquery.databinding.runtime.adapter.DatabindingAdapterUtil
    This class has been deprecated after 0.8.0, can be removed completely later.
    org.eclipse.incquery.databinding.runtime.util.DatabindingUtil
    functionality moved to IncQueryObservables
    org.eclipse.incquery.patternlanguage.emf.specification.GenericPatternMatcher
    direct reference not recommended. As of 0.9, clients should use SpecificationBuilder to convert EMF patterns to IQuerySpecifications, or GenericPatternMatcher for other purposes. Note that the class GenericPatternMatch has also been moved.
